package com.github.bkmbigo.fundaschool.presentation.screens.aboutus

import androidx.compose.material3.Text
import androidx.compose.runtime.Composable

@Composable
fun AboutUsScreenContent(
    onNavigateBack: () -> Unit
) {
    // TODO --> Formatting

    Text(
        text = "Welcome to Fund-a-School: Empowering Education, Transforming Lives!\n" +
                "\n" +
                "At Fund-a-School, we believe that every child deserves access to quality education, regardless of their socio-economic background. Our revolutionary Android application is designed to bridge the gap in educational opportunities by connecting passionate donors with deserving schools and students in need. Through our platform, we strive to create a positive and lasting impact on the lives of countless children, empowering them to reach their full potential and break the cycle of poverty.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "With a deep understanding of the challenges faced by educational institutions in underserved communities, Fund-a-School acts as a catalyst for change. We identify critical needs, such as classroom shortages, lack of resources, inadequate facilities, and limited access to technology, and channel the collective generosity of our donors towards addressing these issues.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "Our mission is simple yet powerful: to unlock the transformative power of education. We firmly believe that education is the key that unlocks doors of opportunity, paving the way for brighter futures and empowering individuals to shape their destinies. By investing in education, we invest in the future of our society.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "Through the Fund-a-School app, donors can browse through a carefully curated list of projects, each carefully vetted and verified by our team. Whether it's funding the construction of classrooms, providing clean water and sanitation facilities, expanding libraries, supporting STEM education, or promoting sports for development, there are various causes to choose from. Donors have the flexibility to select projects that resonate with them and contribute to the specific areas they are passionate about.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "Transparency and accountability are at the core of our values. We ensure that every donated penny is utilized efficiently and effectively, with regular progress updates provided to our donors. Our commitment to accountability extends to our rigorous project evaluation and monitoring processes, ensuring that resources are directed where they are most needed, and the impact is maximized.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "Fund-a-School is more than just a donation platform; it's a community of like-minded individuals who share a common vision of creating a better future through education. We encourage donors to actively engage with the projects they support, fostering personal connections with the schools and students they are helping. By sharing success stories, testimonials, and project updates, we celebrate the collective achievements made possible through the generosity and compassion of our donors.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "We also recognize that education goes beyond the confines of the classroom. That's why we strive to provide holistic support to the schools and students we serve. This includes initiatives to enhance teacher training, improve infrastructure, promote health and nutrition programs, and create safe learning environments.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "Fund-a-School would not be possible without the dedication and support of our donors, partners, and volunteers. We extend our deepest gratitude to all those who have joined us in our mission to make quality education a reality for every child. Together, we are transforming lives, one school, and one student at a time.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "Join us in this noble endeavor. Download the Fund-a-School app today and become a part of a community that is changing lives through the power of education. Together, let's empower the next generation and create a brighter future for all."
    )
